title: Slow message sending
text: It’s a good app to communicate with lots of people all around the world. But the amount of time that it takes to send a message and for it to be delivered is just really slow and needs to be fixed on that.

title: Sending Picture while voice messaging
text:
Hello,
What’s app has been great for plenty of reasons. Thanks for your hard work. 

I only have a request if it’s possible while I am sending a voice message to be able to send a picture at the time. 

As I sometimes was sending a voice at the same time I wanted to share my daughter’s picture with whom I was talking to but unfortunately the voice message will stop. 

Your hardworking on this matter is highly appreciated 

Thank you in advance
